  "description": "This individual is a broad-shouldered human of middle years, marked by bronze skin and steady brown eyes set beneath pronounced brow ridges. Black hair is kept in a plain, close arrangement that emphasizes a square jaw and heavy-cheeked facial structure. Thick fingers and permanently calloused palms testify to a lifetime of repetitive, utilitarian work. A faint, old cut-line crosses one knuckle, the only notable blemish on an otherwise unadorned visage.",
